# Backend Rules

Use typed Python and Pydantic models.

Keep modules small: models.py, knowledge_pack.py, templates.py, generation.py, validators.py, exporters.py.

The first implementation must use MockGenerationProvider.

Do not call real AI APIs in tests. Do not store API keys in code. Do not execute uploaded user files.
